<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: shape_item_relationship
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.shape_item_relationship">
A <b>shape_item_relationship</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> and a  <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item_relationship"/>
that implements the ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Shape_item_relationship"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: shape_item_relationship.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.shape_item_relationship.wr:WR1">
The <b>shape_item_relationship</b> <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item_relationship.relating_representation_item"/> shall not be <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item_relationship.related_representation_item"/>. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: shape_item_relationship.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.shape_item_relationship.wr:WR2">
The <b>shape_item_relationship</b> shall not be a complex subtype of other than its direct supertypes.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: shape_item_relationship.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.shape_item_relationship.ur:UR1">
The combination of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item_relationship.relating_representation_item"/> and <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item_relationship.related_representation_item"/> shall be unique within a population of <b>shape_item_relationship</b>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: feature_shape_definition_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.feature_shape_definition_constraint">
<p>
The <b>feature_shape_definition_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of a 
 <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> when it is used as a <express_ref linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Feature_shape_definition"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: feature_shape_definition_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Extended_elemental_geometric_shape_mim.feature_shape_definition_constraint.wr:WR1"> 
Each instance of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> with a name of 'zone shape' and a dimensionality of 3
shall be a <express_ref linkend="aic_manifold_subsurface:ir_express:aic_manifold_subsurface.manifold_subsurface_shape_representation"/>.
</ext_description>

